0.3
===
* Replaced IStatsCollector with IClacksInstrumentation for better hooks into current state of the server
* Fixed various issues causing errors under load
  * New client and server request processing logic
  * More resilient ConnectionPool
  * Fixed bad Socket.Listen queue size 
* Added auto-reconnect/retry on client request failure (assumes stateless server, can be turned off)
* ClacksClient now requires an IConnectionPool, no longer supports just an ISocket